INSERT OVERWRITE DIRECTORY '/tmp/TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR'
ROW FORMAT DELIMITED FIELDS TERMINATED BY '|' STORED AS TEXTFILE
SELECT TABLA_APR,WF_NAME,WORKFLOW,SUM(
CASE ESTATUS_CRU
WHEN 'PENDIENTE' THEN 1
ELSE '0'
END) as faltante
FROM bddlorg.TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR
GROUP BY TABLA_APR , WF_NAME,WORKFLOW
HAVING faltante=0

                        TCCDMONE, TCTIPMOR, TCTIPMOA, IMPCEC81, CDREFDET, fecontab_fch,
                        NUAPUNTE, INTCOCON,
                        CONCAT('ktom49', INDORI) AS tabori,
                        upper(sistorig) as sistorig
                    from (
                           select 
                                CDSINIES, CTNUPOIN, CDMCT, CDMCR, NUMOVIMI, TCTIPRES, NUMIDTRA, TCTITXCT, TCCDCATR, TCCOPERA, TCDOMORI, TCTINEGO, CDMEDPAG, 
                                TCCDMONE, CDTIPCAM, TCTIPMOR, TCTIPMOA, IMPCEC81, CDREFDET, FECONTAB as fecontab_fch, NUAPUNTE, 
                                INTCOCON, 't' as INDORI, 'INFO' AS sistorig
                            from bddlcru.ktom49t
                             where cdciagru = 'AU' and trim(cdsinies) <>''  and cdsinies = '0071800403'
                          --  ----------  muestra ejemplo  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                          --  and cdsinies in ('0004183174','0000429035','0002716645','0014398184','0071454730','0079342119','0050406990','0049725005',
                          --                   '0075842088','0063900674','0064612880','0067140475','0068016724','0043399450','0044233385','0042004747','0021538996','0044599934',
                          --                   '0042369785','0039068762','0041919481','0043229657','0045723137','0065068777','0059570283','0042219618','0042219618',
                          --                   '0044588176','0045973534','0042923326','0048020655','0042031781','0001005743','0002589919','0000695890','0002528131','0002276830',
                          --                   '0000801373','0002090439','0002009595','0000603928','0001972496'
                          --                   )
                          -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                     union all
                            select
                                CDSINIES, CTNUPOIN, CDMCT, CDMCR, NUMOVIMI, TCTIPRES, NUMIDTRA, TCTITXCT, TCCDCATR, TCCOPERA, TCDOMORI, TCTINEGO, CDMEDPAG, 
                                TCCDMONE, CDTIPCAM, TCTIPMOR, TCTIPMOA, IMPCEC81, CDREFDET, 
                                cast(concat(substr(cast (fecontab as string),1,4),'-',substr(cast (fecontab as string),5,2),'-',substr(cast (fecontab as string),7,2)) as timestamp) as fecontab_fch,
                                NUAPUNTE, INTCOCON, 'h' as INDORI, 'INFO' AS sistorig
                            from bddlcru.ktom49h
                            where cdciagru = 'AU' and trim(cdsinies) <>''  and cdsinies = '0071800403'
                           -- ----------  muestra ejemplo  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                           -- and cdsinies in ('0004183174','0000429035','0002716645','0014398184','0071454730','0079342119','0050406990','0049725005',
                           --                  '0075842088','0063900674','0064612880','0067140475','0068016724','0043399450','0044233385','0042004747','0021538996','0044599934',
                           --                  '0042369785','0039068762','0041919481','0043229657','0045723137','0065068777','0059570283','0042219618','0042219618',
                           --                  '0044588176','0045973534','0042923326','0048020655','0042031781','0001005743','0002589919','0000695890','0002528131','0002276830',
                           --                  '0000801373','0002090439','0002009595','0000603928','0001972496'
                           --                  )
                           -- ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                        ) u
             ) a
            left outer join 
            (
                SELECT    --- Dominio contable    --ok
                    trim(CDELEMEN) AS tcdomori,
                    trim(DSELEMEN) as DSDOMORI
                FROM  BDDLCRU.KTCTGET
                WHERE TRIM(CDTABLA)='KTOT20G' AND CDIDIOMA ='ES'
            ) b
            on (a.tcdomori=b.tcdomori)
            left outer join 
            (
                SELECT    --- Tipo de transaccion contable   --ok
                    substr(TRIM(CDELEMEN),1,2) AS tcdomori,
                    substr(TRIM(CDELEMEN),3,3) AS TCTITXCT,
                    trim(DSELEMEN) as DSTITXCT
                FROM  BDDLCRU.KTCTGET
                WHERE TRIM(CDTABLA)='KTOT51S' AND CDIDIOMA ='ES'
            ) c
            on (a.tcdomori=c.tcdomori and a.TCTITXCT=c.TCTITXCT)
            left outer join 
            (
                SELECT     --- Codigo de operacion contable   --ok
                    substr(TRIM(CDELEMEN),1,2) AS tcdomori,
                    substr(TRIM(CDELEMEN),3,3) AS TCCOPERA,
                    substr(trim(DSELEMEN),1,60) as DSCOPERA
                FROM  BDDLCRU.KTCTGET
                WHERE TRIM(CDTABLA)='KTOT23S' AND CDIDIOMA ='ES'
            ) d
            on (a.tcdomori=d.tcdomori and a.TCCOPERA=d.TCCOPERA)
            left outer join 
            (
                SELECT     --- Codigo de operacion contable   --ok
                    trim(CDELEMEN) AS INTCOCON,
                    trim(DSELEMEN) as DSTCOCON
                FROM  BDDLCRU.KTCTGET
                WHERE TRIM(CDTABLA)='KSITIPG' AND CDIDIOMA ='ES'
            ) e
            on (a.INTCOCON=e.INTCOCON)
            left outer join 
            (
                SELECT --cve_tipo_reserva -- ok
                    TRIM(CDTABLA) AS CDTABLA,
                    trim(CDELEMEN) AS tctipres,
                    trim(DSELEMEN) as dstipres
                FROM  BDDLCRU.KTCTGET
                WHERE TRIM(CDTABLA)='KTOTTRG' AND CDIDIOMA ='ES'
            ) g
            on (a.tctipres=g.tctipres)
            left outer join 
            (
                SELECT   --- cve_medio_pago -- ok
                    substr(TRIM(CDELEMEN),1,2) AS tcdomori,
                    substr(TRIM(CDELEMEN),3,4) AS CDMEDPAG,
                    trim(DSELEMEN) as DSMEDPAG
                FROM  BDDLCRU.KTCTGET
                WHERE TRIM(CDTABLA)='KTOT04S' AND CDIDIOMA ='ES'
            ) i
            on (a.tcdomori=i.tcdomori and a.CDMEDPAG=i.CDMEDPAG)
            left outer join  
            (  --- Nombre y descripcion de cobertura tarificable segun INFO
                SELECT CDMCT, regexp_replace(NOMCT,'DA#O','DAO') as NOMCT_info, regexp_replace(DSMCT,'DA#O','DAO') as DSMCT_info 
                FROM bddlcru.KTPM18T 
            ) k
            on (a.CDMCT=k.CDMCT)
            LEFT OUTER JOIN
            (--- Nombre, descripcion y cobertura agrupada de las coberturas tarificable y afecta segun el catalogo oficial del area tecnica de autos
                select 
                      clave_cobertura_tarificable, 
                      regexp_replace(nombre_cobertura_tarificable,'DAO','DAO')      as nom_CDMCT, 
                      regexp_replace(descripcion_cobertura_tarificable,'DAO','DAO') as desr_CDMCT,
                      clave_cobertura_afecta, 
                      regexp_replace(nombre_cobertura_afecta,'DAO','DAO')      as nom_CDMCR, 
                      regexp_replace(descripcion_cobertura_afecta,'DAO','DAO') as desr_CDMCR,
                      nueva_agrupacion as CDMCR_agr
                from bddldes.coberturas_afectas 
            ) n
            on (trim(n.clave_cobertura_tarificable) = trim(a.CDMCT) and trim(n.clave_cobertura_afecta) = trim(a.CDMCR))
            left outer join ( 
                select distinct trim(from_cur) as from_cur, cast(rate_mult as float) as rate_mult, fecha from bddlint.fnz_tipo_cambio
                where from_cur is not null 
            ) TC
            on (TC.from_cur = trim(a.TCCDMONE) and TC.fecha = a.fecontab_fch)
        )  d

SELECT *,
D.cve_segmento,
D.des_segmento,
'FR' AS VM
FROM (
SELECT 
     A.*
    ,B.ofncve
FROM (SELECT 
    num_poliza,
    vigencia_poliza,
    num_version_poliza
    ,cve_folio,cve_negocio
    ,num_contrato,
    am_emision
From bddlapr.cnm_poliza 
where cve_cobertura_contable in ('031','034')
AND am_emision >=201901
GROUP BY 
   num_poliza,
    vigencia_poliza,
    num_version_poliza
    ,cve_folio,cve_negocio
    ,num_contrato,
    am_emision) A LEFT JOIN 
bddlapr.cat_cagente2 B ON A.cve_folio=B.clnumfol AND A.am_emision=B.am_proc) p  LEFT JOIN  
bddldes.gmm_btm_inf_vm_cvenegoci n on (trim(P.cve_negocio)=trim(N.CDNEGOCI)) LEFT JOIN 
bddlapr.cnm_poliza_datos_adicionales D ON (P.num_poliza=D.num_poliza AND
                                           P.vigencia_poliza=D.vigencia_poliza AND
                                           P.num_version_poliza=D.num_version_poliza)

SELECT par_pol_medio_e_t.*,dir.rfc, dir.cve_nacionalidad, dir.calle, dir.num_exterior, dir.num_interior, dir.punto_referencia,
  dir.apartado_postal, dir.id_direccion, dir.est_direccion, dir.ban_dir_principal, dir.cve_tipo_direccion, dir.cve_pais,
   dir.cve_estado, dir.cve_municipio, dir.cve_colonia, dir.codigo_postal, dir.est_direccion_participante, 20191101 AS fecha_proceso
  FROM (
  SELECT par_pol_medio_e.*,mediot.valor_medio_contacto AS valor_medio_contacto_t, mediot.lada_int, mediot.lada
   FROM (
   SELECT parpolcontra_agen.*,medio.valor_medio_contacto AS valor_medio_contacto_m FROM  (
   
    SELECT parpolcontra.*, agen.id_da,agen.cve_da, agen.cve_funcion_agente, agen.tipo_participante AS tipo_participante_ag,
    agen.rfc AS rfc_ag, agen.cve_nacionalidad AS cve_nacionalidad_ag, agen.nombres AS nombres_ag, agen.apellido_paterno AS apellido_paterno_ag,
    agen.apellido_materno AS apellido_materno_ag, agen.fch_nacimiento AS fch_nacimiento_ag, agen.cve_profesion AS cve_profesion_ag, agen.curp AS curp_ag
    
     FROM (
     
     SELECT parpol.*, contra.nombres, contra.apellido_paterno, contra.apellido_materno, contra.fch_nacimiento, contra.cve_profesion,
      contra.curp, contra.cve_profesion AS cve_actividad_economica FROM (
     
      SELECT par.tipo_participante, TRIM(par.id_participante_consolidado) AS id_participante_consolidado, par.id_participante,
             par.ban_consolidado, crmpol.num_poliza, crmpol.num_version_ult_situacion AS num_version, crmpol.cve_sistema,
             crmpol.cve_estatus_poliza, crmpol.fch_emision, crmpol.fch_inicio_poliza, crmpol.fch_vigencia_inicial,
             crmpol.fch_vigencia_final, crmpol.cve_forma_pago, crmpol.cve_plan_comercial, crmpol.mto_prima_neta, 
             crmpol.mto_prima_total, crmpol.cve_prod_tecnico, crmpol.cve_prod_comercial, crmpol.cve_moneda, crmpol.cve_motivo_movimiento,
             crmpol.cve_conducto_pago, crmpol.mto_prima_pendiente_pago, crmpol.mto_prima_total_deudor  
       FROM bddltrn.adc_t_crm_participante par 
       LEFT JOIN bddltrn.adc_t_crm_polizas crmpol
        ON par.num_poliza = crmpol.num_poliza 
        
       ) AS parpol 
       LEFT JOIN bddltrn.adc_t_crm_contratante contra 
        ON parpol.id_participante = contra.id_participante
    ) AS parpolcontra 
     LEFT JOIN bddltrn.ADC_T_CRM_AGENTE agen 
      ON parpolcontra.num_poliza = agen.num_poliza
     ) AS parpolcontra_agen
     
      LEFT JOIN (
      
       SELECT valor_medio_contacto,id_participante,COUNT(id_participante) AS total 
        FROM bddltrn.ADC_T_CRM_MEDIO_CONTACTO
         WHERE cve_tipo_contacto = "MAIL"
         GROUP BY valor_medio_contacto, id_participante
      ) AS medio
      
     ON parpolcontra_agen.id_participante=medio.id_participante
   ) AS par_pol_medio_e 
      LEFT JOIN (
      
        SELECT valor_medio_contacto, lada_int, lada, id_participante, COUNT(id_participante) AS total 
        FROM bddltrn.ADC_T_CRM_MEDIO_CONTACTO
         WHERE cve_tipo_contacto = "TLPT"
         GROUP BY valor_medio_contacto, lada_int, lada, id_participante
      
      ) AS mediot
       ON par_pol_medio_e.id_participante=mediot.id_participante
  ) AS par_pol_medio_e_t   
     LEFT JOIN bddltrn.ADC_T_CRM_DIRECCION dir
      ON par_pol_medio_e_t.id_participante=dir.id_participante AND par_pol_medio_e_t.num_poliza=dir.num_poliza

CREATE temporary table tmp_canalventas as
SELECT A.*,
B.cve_folio,
B.cve_canal_venta,
B.num_contrato,
B.cve_negocio,
B.am_emision
FROM tmp_conversionmaxima A
LEFT JOIN bddlapr.cnm_poliza  B ON
(A.num_poliza=B.num_poliza AND
A.vigencia_poliza=B.vigencia_poliza AND 
A.num_version_poliza=B.num_version_poliza)

CREATE temporary table tmp_canalventas as
SELECT A.*,
B.cve_folio,
B.cve_canal_venta,
B.num_contrato,
B.cve_negocio,
B.am_emision
FROM tmp_conversionmaxima A
LEFT JOIN bddlapr.cnm_poliza  B ON
(A.num_poliza=B.num_poliza AND
A.vigencia_poliza=B.vigencia_poliza AND

CREATE temporary table tmp_conversionmaxima as
SELECT 
num_poliza,
vigencia_poliza,
num_version_poliza
From bddlapr.cnm_poliza 
where cve_cobertura_contable in ('031','034')
GROUP BY 
num_poliza,
vigencia_poliza,
num_version_poliza

select
CTA.cve_siniestro,
count(CTA.cve_siniestro) cta_siniestros,
CTA.NO_PAGOS,
CTA.IMPORTE,
CTA.tipo_egreso_final,
CTA.tipo_egreso,
CASE WHEN trim(des_supervisoria) in ('Acapulco','Supervisoria Acapulco') THEN 'ACAPULCO'
         WHEN trim(des_supervisoria) in ('Aguascalientes','Supervisoria Aguascalientes') THEN 'AGUASCALIENTES'
         WHEN trim(des_supervisoria) in ('Cancun','Cancn','Supervisoria Cancn','Supervisoria Cancun') THEN 'CANCUN'
         WHEN trim(des_supervisoria) in ('Cd. Juarez','Cd. Jurez','Supervisoria Cd. Jurez','SUPERVISORIA CD.JUAREZ') THEN 'CD. JUAREZ'
         WHEN trim(des_supervisoria) in ('Cd. Obregon','Cd. Obregn','Supervisoria Cd. Obregn','SUPERVISORIA CD.OBREGON') THEN 'CD. OBREGON'
         WHEN trim(des_supervisoria) in ('Chalco','Supervisoria Chalco') THEN 'CHALCO'
         WHEN trim(des_supervisoria) in ('Chihuahua','Supervisoria Chihuahua') THEN 'CHIHUAHUA'
         WHEN trim(des_supervisoria) in ('Coatzacoalcos','Supervisoria Coatzacoalcos') THEN 'COATZACOALCOS'
         WHEN trim(des_supervisoria) in ('Cuernavaca','Supervisoria Cuernavaca') THEN 'CUERNAVACA'
         WHEN trim(des_supervisoria) in ('Culiacan','Culiacn','Supervisoria Culiacan') THEN 'CULIACAN'
         wHEN trim(des_supervisoria) in ('Guadalajara','Supervisoria Culiacn','Supervisoria Guadalajara') THEN 'GUADALAJARA'
         WHEN trim(des_supervisoria) in ('GuadalajaraF.','Supervisoria GuadalajaraF.','Supervisoria Guadalajara F.') THEN 'GUADALAJARAF.' 
         WHEN trim(des_supervisoria) in ('Hermosillo','Supervisoria Hermosillo') THEN 'HERMOSILLO'
         WHEN trim(des_supervisoria) in ('Xalapa','Supervisoria Xalapa','Supervisoria Jalapa') THEN 'XALAPA'
         WHEN trim(des_supervisoria) in ('Leon','Len','Supervisoria Len','Supervisoria Leon') THEN 'LEON'
         WHEN trim(des_supervisoria) in ('Los Mochis','Supervisoria Los Mochis') THEN 'LOS MOCHIS' 
         WHEN trim(des_supervisoria) in ('Merida','Mrida','Supervisoria Mrida','Supervisoria Merida') THEN 'MERIDA' 
         WHEN trim(des_supervisoria) in ('Zona Metro','Plaza_N.P.','Supervisoria Plaza_N.P.','Supervisoria Metropolitano') THEN 'METROPOLITANO' 
         WHEN trim(des_supervisoria) in ('Mexicali','Supervisoria Mexicali') THEN 'MEXICALI' 
         WHEN trim(des_supervisoria) in ('Monterrey','Supervisoria Monterrey') THEN 'MONTERREY' 
         WHEN trim(des_supervisoria) in ('Morelia','Supervisoria Morelia') THEN 'MORELIA' 
         WHEN trim(des_supervisoria) in ('Oaxaca','Supervisoria Oaxaca') THEN 'OAXACA' 
         WHEN trim(des_supervisoria) in ('Pachuca','Supervisoria Pachuca') THEN 'PACHUCA' 
         WHEN trim(des_supervisoria) in ('Puebla','Supervisoria Puebla') THEN 'PUEBLA' 
         WHEN trim(des_supervisoria) in ('Queretaro','Quertaro','Supervisoria Quertaro','Supervisoria Queretaro') THEN 'QUERETARO' 
         WHEN trim(des_supervisoria) in ('Reynosa','Supervisoria Reynosa') THEN 'REYNOSA'

CREATE TABLE bddldes.dauniverso_b as select
  cdnumpol, inancaco, cdprodte, cdprodco, producto, tcforpag, pocoaseg, tccdmone, clfiltom, 
cast(concat(substr(feeftona,1,4) ,'-', substr(feeftona,5,2) ,'-',substr(feeftona,7,2)) as date) as feeftona,
cast(concat(substr(femision,1,4) ,'-', substr(femision,5,2) ,'-',substr(femision,7,2)) as date) as femision,
cast(concat(substr(fevencim,1,4) ,'-', substr(fevencim,5,2) ,'-',substr(fevencim,7,2)) as date) as fevencim,
  cdinterm, folio, cdrfc, nocomple, agente, tccopost, cdgiroes, uscvesus, giro, nombre, plaza, 
  dscanal, dssubcanal, nplaza, ndireccion, clasifica, plaza_redt, redt, gerente, sbdirector, 
  director,id_cuentas, tipo, segmento, tipo_age, fac, bal, apetito_nv, nsegmento, mayor30, 
  prod2, canal, subcanal, i_canal, i_segmento, i_agrupado, i_apetito, i_plazared, i_prodinfo, 
  i_gc, i_jm, i_jr, i_ws, i_corre, cdsuscri
from bddldes.dauniverso

INSERT OVERWRITE DIRECTORY '/tmp/TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR'
ROW FORMAT DELIMITED FIELDS TERMINATED BY '|' STORED AS TEXTFILE
SELECT TABLA_APR,WF_NAME,WORKFLOW,SUM(
CASE ESTATUS_CRU
WHEN 'PENDIENTE' THEN 1
ELSE '0'
END) as faltante
FROM bddlorg.TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR
GROUP BY TABLA_APR , WF_NAME,WORKFLOW
HAVING faltante=0

UPDATE bddlorg.TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR
SET ESTATUS_CRU= 'FINALIZADO',
FECHA_CRU=  FROM_UNIXTIME( UNIX_TIMESTAMP(), 'dd/MM/YYYY HH:mm:ss' )
WHERE TABLA_CRU=UCASE('KREMD5T')

SELECT 
a.id_solicitud,
a.num_poliza,
a.num_version_poliza,
a.cve_cliente_origen,
a.nombre_asegurado,
a.apellido_paterno_asegurado,
a.apellido_materno_asegurado,
a.cve_sistema,
a.nombre_med_tratante,
a.apellido_paterno_med_tratante,
a.apellido_materno_med_tratante,
a.rfc_medico_tratante,
a.cve_pad_icd9_solicitud,
a.des_pad_icd9_solicitud,
a.cve_modalidad,
a.fch_ocurrencia_siniestro,
a.razon_social_proveedor,
b.num_orden_pago,
b.num_consecutivo_orden_pago,
b.num_reclamacion,
b.cve_tipo_gasto,
b.descr_tipo_gasto,
b.cve_estatus_pago,
b.descr_estatus_pago,
b.cve_cliente_origen_beneficiario,
sum(b.mto_total) as mto_total,
b.fch_contable,
b.anio_mes_contable,
b.num_factura_pago,
b.cve_medio_pago,
b.id_proveedor,
b.cve_subconcepto_reserva,
c.folio_comprobante,
d.cve_procedimiento,
d.des_procedimiento,
d.num_cons_procedimiento_aut
FROM cnm_solicitud A
LEFT JOIN bddlapr.cnm_solicitud_pago AS B ON A.id_solicitud = B.id_solicitud
LEFT JOIN cnm_comprobante AS C ON B.id_solicitud = C.id_solicitud 
                               AND B.num_orden_pago = C.num_orden_pago
                               AND B.num_consecutivo_orden_pago = C.num_consecutivo_orden_pago
LEFT JOIN cnm_procedimiento AS D ON A.id_solicitud = D.id_solicitud
--WHERE A.id_solicitud = '0077449692'
WHERE cve_subconcepto_reserva = 'HM'
AND  b.fch_contable between '2019-10-01 00:00:00' and '2019-10-31 00:00:00'
--and d.num_cons_procedimiento_aut = 1
GROUP BY 
a.id_solicitud,
a.num_poliza,
a.num_version_poliza,
a.cve_cliente_origen,
a.nombre_asegurado,
a.apellido_paterno_asegurado,

SELECT TABLA_APR,WF_NAME,WORKFLOW,SUM(
CASE ESTATUS_CRU
WHEN 'PENDIENTE' THEN 1
ELSE '0'
END) as faltante
FROM bddlorg.TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR
GROUP BY TABLA_APR , WF_NAME,WORKFLOW
HAVING faltante=0

create table bddltrn.cnm_comisiones_asegurado_cobertura_base as
select
anio_mes_contable ,
fch_contable ,
num_poliza ,
vigencia_poliza ,
num_version_poliza ,
num_poliza_cobranza ,
num_endoso ,
contador_secuencia_objeto ,
cve_cobertura_contratada ,
des_cobertura_contratada  ,
NVL(cve_asegurado,'') AS cve_asegurado,
identificador_nvo_renovado ,
cve_cobertura_contable ,
forma_pago ,
mto_comision_prima_neta ,
mto_comision_derecho_poliza ,
mto_comision_recargo_pago_fraccionado  ,
mto_isr_comisiones  ,
mto_importe_comision_total  ,
cve_Identificador_intermediario,
des_Identificador_intermediario,
fecha_movimiento_comision  ,
cve_canal_venta_alterno  ,
porcentaje_comision  ,
segmento,
desc_segmento,
negocio,
desc_negocio,
bonos,
desc_bonos,
plan_incentivos,
pol_contr,
desc_pol_contr,
contrb,
pol_prest,
desc_pol_prest,
mot_exc,
desc_mot_exc,
cve_sistema  ,
reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex',
concat(
NVL( num_poliza,'') ,
NVL(cast(vigencia_poliza   as string),''),
NVL(num_endoso ,''),
NVL(cast(contador_secuencia_objeto   as string),'')
))
idmd5  ,
reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex',
concat(
NVL(cast(anio_mes_contable  as string),''),
fch_contable ,
NVL( num_poliza,'') ,
NVL(cast(vigencia_poliza   as string),''),
NVL(cast(num_version_poliza   as string),''),
NVL(num_poliza_cobranza ,''),
NVL(num_endoso ,''),
NVL(cast(contador_secuencia_objeto   as string),''),
NVL(cve_cobertura_contratada ,''),
NVL(des_cobertura_contratada ,''),
NVL(cve_asegurado ,''),
NVL(identificador_nvo_renovado ,''),
NVL(cve_cobertura_contable ,''),
NVL(forma_pago   ,''),
NVL(cast(mto_comision_prima_neta    as string),''),
NVL(cast(mto_comision_derecho_poliza    as string),''),
NVL(cast(mto_comision_recargo_pago_fraccionado     as string),''),
NVL(cast(mto_isr_comisiones     as string),''),
NVL(cast( mto_importe_comision_total     as string),''),
NVL(cve_Identificador_intermediario,''),
NVL(des_Identificador_intermediario,''),
fecha_movimiento_comision  ,
NVL(cve_canal_venta_alterno  ,''),
NVL(cast(porcentaje_comision    as string),''),
NVL(cve_sistema,'')
))
idmd5completo  ,
fechaaud ,
tipo_comision
from (
SELECT
distinct
anio_mes_contable ,
fch_contable ,
num_poliza ,
vigencia_poliza ,
num_version_poliza ,
num_poliza_cobranza ,
num_endoso ,
contador_secuencia_objeto ,
cve_cobertura_contratada ,
descr_cobertura_contratada     as des_cobertura_contratada,
cve_asegurado ,
identificador_nvo_renovado ,
cve_cobertura_contable ,
forma_pago ,
mto_comision_prima_neta ,
mto_comision_derecho_poliza ,
mto_comision_recargo_pago_fraccionado  ,
mto_isr_comisiones  ,
mto_importe_comision_total  ,
cve_Identificador_intermediario,
des_Identificador_intermediario,
fecha_movimiento_comision  ,
cve_canal_venta_alterno  ,
porcentaje_comision  ,
segmento,
desc_segmento,
negocio,
desc_negocio,
bonos,
desc_bonos,
plan_incentivos,
pol_contr,
desc_pol_contr,
contrb,
pol_prest,
desc_pol_prest,
mot_exc,
desc_mot_exc,
cve_sistema  ,
fechaaud ,
tipo_comision
from bddltrn.cnm_comisiones_asegurado_cobertura
where anio_mes_contable=201505 and
trim(cve_sistema) in ('CBZA','INFO') and tipo_comision='emitida'
union all
SELECT
anio_mes_contable ,
fch_contable ,
num_poliza ,
vigencia_poliza ,
num_version_poliza ,
num_poliza_cobranza ,
num_endoso ,
contador_secuencia_objeto ,
cve_cobertura_contratada ,
descr_cobertura_contratada     as des_cobertura_contratada,
cve_asegurado ,
identificador_nvo_renovado ,
cve_cobertura_contable ,
forma_pago ,
sum(mto_comision_prima_neta) mto_comision_prima_neta ,
sum(mto_comision_derecho_poliza) mto_comision_derecho_poliza,
sum(mto_comision_recargo_pago_fraccionado)  mto_comision_recargo_pago_fraccionado,
sum(mto_isr_comisiones) mto_isr_comisiones ,
sum(mto_importe_comision_total)  mto_importe_comision_total,
cve_Identificador_intermediario,
des_Identificador_intermediario,
fecha_movimiento_comision  ,
cve_canal_venta_alterno  ,
sum(porcentaje_comision)   porcentaje_comision,
segmento,
desc_segmento,
negocio,
desc_negocio,
bonos,
desc_bonos,
plan_incentivos,
pol_contr,
desc_pol_contr,
contrb,
pol_prest,
desc_pol_prest,
mot_exc,
desc_mot_exc,
cve_sistema  ,
fechaaud ,
tipo_comision
from bddltrn.cnm_comisiones_asegurado_cobertura
where anio_mes_contable=201505 and
trim(cve_sistema) in ('CBZA','INFO') and tipo_comision='pagada'
group by
anio_mes_contable ,
fch_contable ,
num_poliza ,

select "", CVE_SISTEMA, "", "", FCH_CONTABLE, "", "", TIPO_CAMBIO_PROM, "", "", MTO_IMPORTE_SINIESTRAL, "" FROM ( SELECT CVE_SISTEMA ,CAST(FCH_CONTABLE AS CHAR(10)) AS FCH_CONTABLE ,CAST(TIPO_CAMBIO_PROM AS DECIMAL(34,4)) AS TIPO_CAMBIO_PROM ,CAST(SUM(MTO_IMPORTE_SINIESTRAL) AS DECIMAL(34,3)) AS MTO_IMPORTE_SINIESTRAL FROM (SELECT CVE_SISTEMA,FCH_CONTABLE,AVG(TIPO_CAMBIO) OVER (PARTITION BY FCH_CONTABLE) AS TIPO_CAMBIO_PROM,MTO_IMPORTE_SINIESTRAL FROM BDDLALM.ALM_SOLICITUD_PAGO WHERE BAN_CONTABLE = 1 AND CVE_SISTEMA = 'INFO' AND FCH_CONTABLE <= DATE_SUB(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(),1) ) T GROUP BY CVE_SISTEMA,FCH_CONTABLE,TIPO_CAMBIO_PROM ORDER BY CVE_SISTEMA,FCH_CONTABLE DESC LIMIT 5 UNION ALL SELECT CVE_SISTEMA ,CAST(FCH_CONTABLE AS CHAR(10)) AS FCH_CONTABLE ,CAST(TIPO_CAMBIO_PROM AS DECIMAL(34,4)) AS TIPO_CAMBIO_PROM ,CAST(SUM(MTO_IMPORTE_SINIESTRAL) AS DECIMAL(34,3)) AS MTO_IMPORTE_SINIESTRAL FROM (SELECT CVE_SISTEMA,FCH_CONTABLE,AVG(TIPO_CAMBIO) OVER (PARTITION BY FCH_CONTABLE) AS TIPO_CAMBIO_PROM,MTO_IMPORTE_SINIESTRAL FROM BDDLALM.ALM_SOLICITUD_PAGO WHERE BAN_CONTABLE = 1 AND CVE_SISTEMA = 'RCLA' AND FCH_CONTABLE <= DATE_SUB(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(),1) ) T GROUP BY CVE_SISTEMA,FCH_CONTABLE,TIPO_CAMBIO_PROM ORDER BY CVE_SISTEMA,FCH_CONTABLE DESC LIMIT 5 ) AS D

INSERT OVERWRITE DIRECTORY '/tmp/TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR'
ROW FORMAT DELIMITED FIELDS TERMINATED BY '|' STORED AS TEXTFILE
SELECT TABLA_APR,WF_NAME,WORKFLOW,SUM(
CASE ESTATUS_CRU
WHEN 'PENDIENTE' THEN 1
ELSE '0'
END) as faltante
FROM bddlorg.TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR
GROUP BY TABLA_APR , WF_NAME,WORKFLOW
HAVING faltante=0

INSERT OVERWRITE DIRECTORY '/tmp/TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR'
ROW FORMAT DELIMITED FIELDS TERMINATED BY '|' STORED AS TEXTFILE
SELECT TABLA_APR,WF_NAME,WORKFLOW,SUM(
CASE ESTATUS_CRU
WHEN 'PENDIENTE' THEN 1
ELSE '0'
END) as faltante
FROM bddlorg.TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR
GROUP BY TABLA_APR , WF_NAME,WORKFLOW
HAVING faltante=0

UPDATE bddlorg.TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR
SET ESTATUS_CRU= 'FINALIZADO',
FECHA_CRU=  FROM_UNIXTIME( UNIX_TIMESTAMP(), 'dd/MM/YYYY HH:mm:ss' )
WHERE TABLA_CRU=UCASE('NRLTRSV0H')

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_F2_CNM_PRIMA_EMITIDA_POLIZA_ENDOSO_DLT AS
SELECT
CASE WHEN anio_mes_contable=0 THEN 140001 ELSE anio_mes_contable END AS anio_mes_contable,
CASE WHEN fch_contable IS NULL THEN CAST("1400-01-01 00:00:00" AS TIMESTAMP) ELSE fch_contable END AS fch_contable,
num_poliza,
vigencia_poliza,
num_version_poliza,
num_poliza_cobranza,
num_endoso,
forma_pago,
cve_tipo_endoso,
mto_prima_tecnica,
mto_recargo_descuento,
mto_prima_neta,
mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado,
pct_pago_prima,
mto_prima_neta_sin_pago_fracc,
mto_recargo_nvo_met_pago,
mto_derecho_poliza,
mto_cesion_comision,
mto_iva_poliza,
mto_prima_total,
cve_cobertura_contable,
CASE WHEN fch_emision IS NULL THEN CAST("1400-01-01 00:00:00" AS TIMESTAMP) ELSE fch_emision END AS fch_emision,
NVL(segmento, '') AS segmento,
NVL(desc_segmento, '') AS desc_segmento,
NVL(negocio, '') AS negocio,
NVL(desc_negocio, '') AS desc_negocio,
NVL(bonos, '') AS bonos,
NVL(desc_bonos, '') AS desc_bonos,
NVL(plan_incentivos, '') AS plan_incentivos,
NVL(pol_contr, '') AS pol_contr,
NVL(desc_pol_contr, '') AS desc_pol_contr,
NVL(contrb, '') AS contrb,
NVL(pol_prest, '') AS pol_prest,
NVL(desc_pol_prest, '') AS desc_pol_prest,
NVL(mot_exc, '') AS mot_exc,
NVL(desc_mot_exc, '') AS desc_mot_exc,
cve_canal_venta_alterno,
reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex',concat(NVL(num_poliza,''), CAST(NVL(CAST(vigencia_poliza AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(num_version_poliza AS INT),0) AS STRING),NVL(num_poliza_cobranza,''), NVL(num_endoso,''))) AS idmd5,
reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex',concat(
NVL(num_poliza,''), CAST(NVL(CAST(vigencia_poliza AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(num_version_poliza AS INT),0) AS STRING),NVL(num_poliza_cobranza,''), NVL(num_endoso,''),
NVL(forma_pago,'') ,NVL(cve_tipo_endoso,''),CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_prima_tecnica AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_recargo_descuento AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_prima_neta AS INT),0) AS STRING),
CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_cesion_comision AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(pct_pago_prima AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_prima_neta_sin_pago_fracc AS INT),0) AS STRING),
CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_recargo_nvo_met_pago AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_derecho_poliza AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_iva_poliza AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_prima_total AS INT),0) AS STRING),
NVL(cve_cobertura_contable,''), CAST(NVL(CAST(anio_mes_contable AS INT),0) AS STRING))) as idmd5completo,
from_unixtime(unix_timestamp()) AS FECHAAUD,
cve_sistema_int
FROM(
select * from  BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_F2_PRIMA_EMITIDA_DLT
) AS STG_POLIZA_ENDOSO_GMM_PRIMA_EMITIDA
ORDER BY fch_contable,num_poliza,num_version_poliza, cve_sistema_int

CREATE TABLE BDDLTRN.STG_INFO_POLIZA_ENDOSO_GMM_PRIMA_EMITIDA as
SELECT
CAST(anio_mes_contable AS INT) AS anio_mes_contable ,
CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTR(fecha_contable,1,4),"-",SUBSTR(fecha_contable,5,2),"-",SUBSTR(fecha_contable,7,2)," 00:00:00") AS timestamp) as fch_contable ,
CAST (num_poliza as varchar(14)) as num_poliza ,
CAST (indicador_vigencia as int) as vigencia_poliza,
CAST (num_version_poliza as int) as num_version_poliza  ,
CAST ('' as varchar(8)) as num_poliza_cobranza  ,
CAST ('' as varchar(6)) as num_endoso  ,
CAST (forma_pago as String) as forma_pago,
CAST ('' as varchar(3)) as cve_tipo_endoso,
CAST (SUM(mto_prima_tecnica) AS DECIMAL(20,6)) as mto_prima_tecnica,
CAST (SUM(mto_recargo_descuento) AS DECIMAL(20,6)) as mto_recargo_descuento,
CAST (SUM(mto_prima_neta)AS DECIMAL(20,6))  as mto_prima_neta,
CAST (SUM(mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado)AS DECIMAL(20,6)) as mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado,
CAST (pct_pago_prima AS DECIMAL(11,6)) as pct_pago_prima ,
CAST (SUM(mto_prima_neta_sin_pago_fracc) AS DECIMAL(20,6)) as mto_prima_neta_sin_pago_fracc,
CAST (SUM(mto_recargo_nvo_met_pago) AS DECIMAL(20,6)) as mto_recargo_nvo_met_pago,
CAST (SUM(mto_derecho_poliza) AS DECIMAL(20,6)) as mto_derecho_poliza,
CAST (SUM(mto_cesion_comision) AS DECIMAL(20,6))  as mto_cesion_comision,
CAST (SUM(mto_iva_poliza) AS DECIMAL(20,6)) as mto_iva_poliza,
CAST (SUM(mto_prima_total) AS DECIMAL(20,6)) as mto_prima_total,
CAST(SUBSTR (cve_cobertura_contable,2,3) as varchar(3)) as cve_cobertura_contable,
CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTR(fecha_emision,1,4),"-",SUBSTR(fecha_emision,5,2),"-",SUBSTR(fecha_emision,7,2)) AS timestamp) as fch_emision,
CAST(segmento AS VARCHAR(300)) AS segmento,
CAST(desc_segmento AS VARCHAR(300)) AS desc_segmento,
CAST(negocio AS VARCHAR(300)) AS negocio,
CAST(desc_negocio AS VARCHAR(300)) AS desc_negocio,
CAST(bonos AS VARCHAR(300)) AS bonos,
CAST(desc_bonos AS VARCHAR(300)) AS desc_bonos,
CAST(plan_incentivos AS VARCHAR(300)) AS plan_incentivos,
CAST(pol_contr AS VARCHAR(300)) AS pol_contr,
CAST(desc_pol_contr AS VARCHAR(300)) AS desc_pol_contr,
CAST(contrb AS VARCHAR(300)) AS contrb,
CAST(pol_prest AS VARCHAR(300)) AS pol_prest,
CAST(desc_pol_prest AS VARCHAR(300)) AS desc_pol_prest,
CAST(mot_exc AS VARCHAR(300)) AS mot_exc,
CAST(desc_mot_exc AS VARCHAR(300)) AS desc_mot_exc,
'' as cve_canal_venta_alterno,
CAST('' AS VARCHAR(32)) AS IDMD5,
CAST('' AS VARCHAR(32)) AS IDMD5COMPLETO,
CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS fechaaud,
CAST('INFO' AS VARCHAR(10)) AS cve_sistema_int
FROM BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_F2_IMPORTE_FILTER  as importe
group by num_poliza,
num_version_poliza,
anio_mes_contable,
cve_cobertura_contable,
segmento,
desc_segmento,
negocio,
desc_negocio,
bonos,
desc_bonos,
plan_incentivos,
pol_contr,
desc_pol_contr,
contrb,
pol_prest,
desc_pol_prest,
mot_exc,
desc_mot_exc,
indicador_vigencia,
fecha_contable,
forma_pago,
fecha_emision,
pct_pago_prima
ORDER BY  fch_contable,cve_sistema_int,num_poliza,num_version_poliza

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_F2_IMPORTE_FILTER as
SELECT
substr(CAST(FECONTAB AS string),1,6) as anio_mes_contable,
CAST(FECONTAB as String) as fecha_contable,
CDNUMPOL as num_poliza,
CTVRSPOL as num_version_poliza,
INANCACO as indicador_vigencia,
CDMCT as cobertura_contable,
CDOBJTP as objeto_codigo,
CTSECOBJ as objeto_secuencia,
TCFORPAG as forma_pago,
SIGNO * PRTECNICA as mto_prima_tecnica,
SIGNO * (PRNETA - PRTECNICA)   as mto_recargo_descuento,
SIGNO * PRNETA  as mto_prima_neta,
SIGNO * (IMREFRAC1 + IMREFRAC2) as mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado,
PORCNFP as pct_pago_prima,
SIGNO * PRNETANFP as mto_prima_neta_sin_pago_fracc,
CASE WHEN PORCNFP > 0 THEN SIGNO * (PRNETA  - PRNETANFP) else (SIGNO * PRNETA)  END as mto_recargo_nvo_met_pago,
SIGNO * IMDERPOL as mto_derecho_poliza,
-1 * SIGNO * PRCEDIDA as mto_cesion_comision,
SIGNO * (IMIVA + GAIVA )as mto_iva_poliza,
SIGNO * (PRNETA - PRCEDIDA +IMREFRAC1 + IMREFRAC2 + IMDERPOL + IMIVA + GAIVA) as mto_prima_total,
CDRAMDGS as cve_cobertura_contable,
nvl(segmento,'') as segmento,
nvl(desc_segmento,'') as desc_segmento,
nvl(negocio,'') as negocio,
nvl(desc_negocio,'') as desc_negocio,
nvl(bonos,'') as bonos,
nvl(desc_bonos,'') as desc_bonos,
nvl(plan_incentivos,'') as plan_incentivos,
nvl(pol_contr,'') as pol_contr,
nvl(desc_pol_contr,'') as desc_pol_contr,
nvl(contrb,0) as contrb,
nvl(pol_prest,'') as pol_prest,
nvl(desc_pol_prest,'') as desc_pol_prest,
nvl(mot_exc,'') as mot_exc,
nvl(desc_mot_exc,'') as desc_mot_exc,
CAST(FEMISION as String) AS fecha_emision
FROM BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_F2_KTOM41T_FILTER  as ktom41t
order by fecha_contable, num_poliza,num_version_poliza

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_F2_KTOM41T_FILTER AS
SELECT
ktom41t.CDNUMPOL,
ktom41t.CTVRSPOL,
ktom41t.CDRAMDGS,
kcim06t.INANCACO,
catalogo.DSFORPAG as TCFORPAG,
ktom41t.cdmct,
ktom41t.cdobjtp,
ktom41t.ctsecobj,
case when ktom41t.TCCOPERA= '003' then  -1 else  1 end as SIGNO,
ktom41t.impcec01 as PRTECNICA ,
ktom41t.impcec02 as PRCEDIDA,
ktom41t.impcec03 as IMREFRAC1,
ktom41t.impcec04 as IMDERPOL,
ktom41t.impcec05 as IMIVA ,
ktom41t.impcec06 as GAIVA ,
ktom41t.impcec07 as IMREFRAC2,
ktom41t.Impcec19 as PRNETA ,
ktom41t.impcec20 as PRTOTAL ,
KCIM16T.IMCAAP15 as PORCNFP,
(IMPCEC19 * (KCIM16T.IMCAAP15 / 100)) AS  PRNETANFP,
CASE WHEN (KCIM06T.FEMISION=0 OR KCIM06T.FEMISION IS NULL ) THEN 14000101 ELSE KCIM06T.FEMISION END AS FEMISION,
CASE WHEN FECONTAB<14000101 THEN 14000101 ELSE FECONTAB END AS FECONTAB,
CAST(NVL(CAST(gmmep.CDETISEG AS STRING), '')AS STRING) AS SEGMENTO,
CAST(NVL(CAST(KTCTGETSEG.dselemen AS STRING), '')AS STRING) as desc_segmento,
CAST(NVL(CAST(gmmep.CDNEGMUL AS STRING), '')AS STRING) AS NEGOCIO,
CAST(NVL(CAST(KTCTGETMUL.dselemen AS STRING), '')AS STRING) as desc_negocio,
CAST(NVL(CAST(gmmep.CDTIPBON AS STRING), '')AS STRING) AS BONOS,
CAST(NVL(CAST(KTCTGETBON.dselemen AS STRING), '')AS STRING) as desc_bonos,
CASE WHEN (KCIM06T.INPOLPAI = 'N') THEN 'True' ELSE 'False' END AS PLAN_INCENTIVOS,
CAST(NVL(CAST(gmmep.INPOLCON AS STRING), '')AS STRING) AS POL_CONTR,
CAST(NVL(CAST(KTCTGETPCO.dselemen AS STRING), '')AS STRING) as desc_pol_contr,
CAST(gmmep.PORCONTR AS INT) AS CONTRB,
CAST(NVL(CAST(gmmep.INPOLPRE AS STRING), '')AS STRING) AS POL_PREST,
CAST(NVL(CAST(KTCTGETPPR.dselemen AS STRING), '')AS STRING) as desc_pol_prest,
CAST(NVL(CAST(KCIM06T.INPOLPAI AS STRING), '')AS STRING)  AS MOT_EXC,
CAST(NVL(CAST(KTCTGETMOT.dselemen AS STRING), '')AS STRING) as desc_mot_exc
FROM (SELECT * FROM BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_F2_KTOM41  ) as ktom41t
INNER JOIN
(SELECT distinct CDNUMPOL, CTVRSPOL, INANCACO, TCFORPAG,FEMISION, INPOLPAI
FROM bddlcru.kcim06t WHERE cdciagru='SA' and cdprodte like 'G%'
UNION ALL
SELECT distinct CDNUMPOL, CTVRSPOL, INANCACO, TCFORPAG,FEMISION, INPOLPAI
FROM bddlcru.kcim06H WHERE cdciagru='SA' and cdprodte like 'G%'
) AS KCIM06T
ON KTOM41T.cdnumpol=KCIM06T.cdnumpol
AND KTOM41T.ctvrspol=KCIM06T.ctvrspol
LEFT JOIN
(SELECT trim(CDELEMEN) AS CDFORPAG, TRIM(SUBSTR(DSELEMEN,1,30)) AS DSFORPAG
FROM bddlcru.KTCTGET WHERE trim(CDTABLA)='KCIT27S' AND trim(CDIDIOMA)='ES') AS   CATALOGO
ON CATALOGO.CDFORPAG = KCIM06T.TCFORPAG
LEFT JOIN
(SELECT distinct CDNUMPOL, CTVRSPOL,IMCAAP15
FROM bddlcru.kcim16t  WHERE NURELREP = 1 and CDPRODTE like 'G%'
UNION ALL
SELECT distinct CDNUMPOL, CTVRSPOL,IMCAAP15
FROM bddlcru.kcim16h  WHERE NURELREP = 1 and CDPRODTE like 'G%'
) as KCIM16T
ON KTOM41T.cdnumpol=KCIM16T.cdnumpol
AND KTOM41T.ctvrspol=KCIM16T.ctvrspol
left join bddlalm.gmm_elemento_poliza gmmep
on ktom41t.CDNUMPOL = TRIM(gmmep.num_poliza) and ktom41t.CTVRSPOL = gmmep.num_version
left join (select cdelemen, dselemen from bddlcru.KTCTGET where trim(cdtabla) =  'KTPTGXG') as KTCTGETSEG on  CAST(TRIM(gmmep.CDETISEG) AS STRING) = TRIM(KTCTGETSEG.cdelemen)
left join (select cdelemen, dselemen from bddlcru.KTCTGET where trim(cdtabla) =  'KCDTECG') as KTCTGETMOT on  CAST(TRIM(KCIM06T.INPOLPAI) AS STRING)= TRIM(KTCTGETMOT.cdelemen)
left join (select cdelemen, dselemen from bddlcru.KTCTGET where trim(cdtabla) =  'KTPTGYG') as KTCTGETMUL on  CAST(TRIM(gmmep.CDNEGMUL) AS STRING) = TRIM(KTCTGETMUL.cdelemen)
left join (select cdelemen, dselemen from bddlcru.KTCTGET where trim(cdtabla) =  'KTPTGZG') as KTCTGETBON on  CAST(TRIM(gmmep.CDTIPBON) AS STRING)= TRIM(KTCTGETBON.cdelemen)
left join (select cdelemen, dselemen from bddlcru.KTCTGET where trim(cdtabla) =  'KTCTSNG') as KTCTGETPCO on  CAST(TRIM(gmmep.INPOLCON) AS STRING) = TRIM(KTCTGETPCO.cdelemen)
left join (select cdelemen, dselemen from bddlcru.KTCTGET where trim(cdtabla) =  'KTCTSNG') as KTCTGETPPR on  CAST(TRIM(gmmep.INPOLPRE) AS STRING) = TRIM(KTCTGETPPR.cdelemen)

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE bddlint.stg_gmm_cdc_alm_recibo_delta
SELECT Z.*
FROM
(
SELECT  stg.*
FROM    bddlalm.alm_recibo           actual
INNER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo    stg ON
actual.idmd5         =   stg.idmd5
WHERE   NVL(actual.idmd5completo,'') <>  NVL(stg.idmd5completo,'')
UNION ALL
SELECT  stg.*
FROM    bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo        stg
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlalm.alm_recibo actual ON
stg.idmd5 = actual.idmd5
WHERE   actual.idmd5 IS NULL
) Z

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE bddlint.stg_gmm_cdc_alm_recibo_con_cambios
SELECT  actual.*, CAST(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp()) AS TIMESTAMP) fechahis
FROM    bddlalm.alm_recibo        actual
INNER JOIN (SELECT idmd5, CAST(NVL(idmd5completo,'') AS VARCHAR(32)) idmd5completo FROM  bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo ) stg ON
actual.idmd5 = stg.idmd5
WHERE   actual.idmd5completo IS NOT NULL
AND actual.idmd5completo <> stg.idmd5completo

CAST('' AS VARCHAR(10))                                       	AS  cve_folio_agente_2,
CAST('' AS VARCHAR(10))                                       	AS  cve_folio_agente_3,
CAST(NVL(RTRIM(cat.cve_canal_cobro), '') AS VARCHAR(20))		AS 	cve_canal_cobro,
CAST(NVL(ban.cdbanco,'') 			AS VARCHAR( 4))				AS  cve_banco,
CAST(NVL(mc.cve_medio_cobro,'') 	AS VARCHAR( 3))				AS	cve_medio_cobro,
CAST(NVL(mc.descr_medio_cobro,'') 	AS VARCHAR(30))				AS 	descr_medio_cobro,
pol.cve_cobertura_contable                                      AS  cve_cobertura_contable,
CAST(NVL(rec.cve_estado_recibo_anterior, '') AS VARCHAR(13))    AS  cve_estado_recibo_anterior,
cat.descr_estado_recibo_anterior,
CAST(NVL(rec.cve_estado_recibo, '') AS varchar(1))				AS  cve_estado_recibo,
cat.descr_estado_recibo,
CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP)                                         AS  fch_cambio_estado,
rec.fch_emision,
rec.fch_inicio_vigencia_recibo,
CAST(
NVL(CONCAT(SUBSTR(CAST(n50.fch_movimiento AS STRING), 1,4), '-',
SUBSTR(CAST(n50.fch_movimiento    AS STRING), 5,2), '-',
SUBSTR(CAST(n50.fch_movimiento    AS STRING), 7,2),
' 00:00:00'), '1400-01-01 00:00:00.000')
AS TIMESTAMP)                                               AS  fch_movimiento,
CAST(
NVL(CASE
WHEN rec.cve_estado_recibo = 'L'   AND fch_p.fch_pago > 0
THEN
CONCAT(SUBSTR(CAST(fch_p.fch_pago AS STRING), 1,4), '-',
SUBSTR(CAST(fch_p.fch_pago    AS STRING), 5,2), '-',
SUBSTR(CAST(fch_p.fch_pago    AS STRING), 7,2),
' 00:00:00')
ELSE NULL
END, '1400-01-01 00:00:00.000')
AS TIMESTAMP)                                               AS  fch_pago,
rec.fch_fin_vigencia_recibo,
CAST(NVL(rec.cve_forma_pago, '') 	AS VARCHAR( 1))				AS  cve_forma_pago,
CAST(NVL(cat.descr_forma_pago, '') 	AS VARCHAR(30))				AS  descr_forma_pago,
CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(15,3))                                     AS  mto_comision,
CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(15,3))                                     AS  mto_comision_recargo,
CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(15,3))                                     AS  mto_comision_derecho_poliza,
CAST(0 AS DECIMAL(13,2))                                        AS  mto_descuento_volumen,
CAST(imp.iva        AS DECIMAL(15,3))                           AS  mto_iva,
CAST(imp.recargos   AS DECIMAL(15,3))                           AS  mto_recargo,
CAST(imp.derechos   AS DECIMAL(15,3))                           AS  mto_derecho_poliza,
CAST(imp.prima_neta AS DECIMAL(15,3))                           AS  mto_prima_neta,
rec.mto_total_pago,
CAST(NVL(rec.cve_ind_nivel_emision, '')   	AS 	VARCHAR( 1))  	AS	cve_ind_nivel_emision,
CAST(NVL(rec.descr_ind_nivel_emision, '') 	AS 	VARCHAR(15)) 	AS	descr_ind_nivel_emision,
CAST(NVL(rec.cve_ind_tipo_movimiento, '') 	AS 	VARCHAR( 1)) 	AS	cve_ind_tipo_movimiento,
CAST(NVL(rec.descr_ind_tipo_movimiento, '') AS 	VARCHAR(15)) 	AS descr_ind_tipo_movimiento,
CAST(''   AS VARCHAR(6))                                        AS  num_endoso,
rec.num_fraccion_pago_poliza,
rec.num_poliza,
rec.num_recibo,
CAST(''   AS VARCHAR(8))                                        AS  num_poliza_cobranza,
CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(15,3))                                     AS  pct_comision,
CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(15,3))                                     AS  pct_participacion_agente_1,
CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(15,3))                                     AS  pct_participacion_agente_2,
CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(15,3))                                     AS  pct_participacion_agente_3,
CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(15,3))                                     AS  mto_prima_total,
CAST(NVL(rec.cve_tipo_transaccion, '') 	 AS	VARCHAR( 2))		AS	cve_tipo_transaccion,
CAST(NVL(cat.descr_tipo_transaccion, '') AS	VARCHAR(40)) 		AS	descr_tipo_transaccion,
rec.num_version_poliza,
rec.vigencia_poliza,
CAST('INFO' AS VARCHAR( 4))                                     AS  cve_sistema,
CAST(NULL   AS VARCHAR( 4))                                     AS  cve_sistema_int,
CAST(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp()) AS TIMESTAMP)              AS  fechaaud,
rec.ori_registro,
rec.fechaaud_registro,
reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex', CAST(rec.num_recibo AS STRING)) AS idmd5,
reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex',
CONCAT(NVL(pol.cve_folio_agente_1,'')
, NVL(cat.cve_canal_cobro,''), NVL(ban.CDBANCO,''), NVL(cve_medio_cobro,''), NVL(descr_medio_cobro,''), cve_cobertura_contable
, NVL(cve_estado_recibo_anterior,''), NVL(cat.descr_estado_recibo_anterior,''), NVL(cve_estado_recibo,''), NVL(cat.descr_estado_recibo,'')
, NVL(CAST(n50.fch_movimiento AS STRING),''), NVL(CAST(fch_p.fch_pago AS STRING),''), NVL(rec.cve_forma_pago,''), NVL(cat.descr_forma_pago,'')
, NVL(CAST(imp.iva AS STRING),''), NVL(CAST(imp.recargos AS STRING),''), NVL(CAST(imp.derechos AS STRING),''), NVL(CAST(imp.prima_neta AS STRING),'')
, NVL(CAST(rec.mto_total_pago AS STRING),''), NVL(rec.cve_ind_nivel_emision,''), NVL(rec.descr_ind_nivel_emision,''), NVL(rec.cve_ind_tipo_movimiento,'')
, NVL(rec.descr_ind_tipo_movimiento,''), NVL(CAST(rec.num_fraccion_pago_poliza AS STRING),''), rec.num_poliza, NVL(rec.num_recibo,'')
, NVL(rec.cve_tipo_transaccion,''), NVL(cat.descr_tipo_transaccion,''), rec.num_version_poliza, rec.vigencia_poliza
))                                                      AS idmd5completo
FROM bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info rec
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_poliza pol ON
rec.num_poliza          = pol.num_poliza
AND rec.num_version_poliza  = pol.num_version_poliza
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_importe imp ON
rec.num_recibo = imp.num_recibo
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_n50 AS n50  ON
rec.num_recibo = n50.num_recibo
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_medio_cobro mc ON
rec.num_recibo = mc.num_recibo
AND rec.cve_estado_recibo   = 'L'
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_cve_banco ban ON
rec.num_recibo          = ban.num_recibo
AND rec.tccancob            = 'BC'
AND rec.cve_estado_recibo   = 'L'
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_fch_pago fch_p ON
rec.num_recibo = fch_p.num_recibo
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_catalogos cat ON
rec.num_recibo = cat.num_recibo

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE bddlint.stg_gmm_cdc_alm_poliza_azul_delta

FROM    bddlalm.alm_poliza_azul           actual
INNER JOIN bddltrn.stg_gmm_poliza_azul_final    stg ON
actual.idmd5         =   stg.idmd5
WHERE   NVL(actual.idmd5completo,'') <>  NVL(stg.idmd5completo,'')

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_medio_cobro2
SELECT t1.cdnumrec, t1.numoveco, t1.nucobpar
FROM bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_medio_cobro1 t1
INNER JOIN (
SELECT cdnumrec, MAX(imremeco) MAX_IMREMECO
FROM bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_medio_cobro1 a1
GROUP BY cdnumrec
) T2 ON
t1.cdnumrec = t2.cdnumrec
AND t1.imremeco = T2.MAX_IMREMECO
